block content

  article.entry
    // header
    .entry-content
      //title
      .bg-yellow
        .container.pt-lg-8.pt-md-7.pt-5.pb-lg-6
              .row.gx-lg-5.gx-md-5.gy-5
                  .col-lg-2.mb-2.mb-lg-0
                      a(href='#ai-for-health')
                          .bg-gray-500.text-white.h-100
                              .text-center.align-items-center
                                  .px-lg-4.py-lg-2.px-4.py-2
                                      .mt-lg-4.mt-5
                                          h3 >
                                          h5.text-uppercase Reports
                  .col-lg-2.mb-2.mb-lg-0
                      a(href='#ai-for-health')
                          .bg-black.text-white.h-100
                              .text-center.align-items-center
                                  .px-lg-4.py-lg-2.px-4.py-2
                                      .mt-lg-4.mt-5
                                          h3.text-uppercase 1.
                                          h5.text-uppercase AI for Health
                  .col-lg-2.mb-2.mb-lg-0
                      a(href='#ai-for-finance')
                          .bg-black.text-white.h-100
                              .text-center.align-items-center
                                  .px-lg-4.py-lg-2.px-4.py-2
                                      .mt-lg-4.mt-5
                                          h3.text-uppercase 2.
                                          h5.text-uppercase AI for Finance
                  .col-lg-2.mb-2.mb-lg-0
                      a(href='#human-in-the-loop')
                          .bg-black.text-white.h-100
                              .text-center.align-items-center
                                  .px-lg-4.py-lg-2.px-4.py-2
                                      .mt-lg-4.mt-5.mb-4
                                          h3.text-uppercase 3.
                                          h5.text-uppercase Human in the loop
                  .col-lg-2.mb-2.mb-lg-0
                      a(href='#interactive-ai')
                          .bg-black.text-white.h-100
                              .text-center.align-items-center
                                  .px-lg-4.py-lg-2.px-4.py-2
                                      .mt-lg-4.mt-5.mb-4
                                          h3.text-uppercase 4.
                                          h5.text-uppercase Interactive AI

    .entry-content.mb-6
        .container
            .row.justify-content-lg-center
                .col-lg-6
                    h4 Reports:
                    p Welcome to our Report Section. Here, we provide you with comprehensive reports that showcase the remarkable progress made by the XAI Project in various domains.
                    p Within this section, you will find a wealth of information highlighting our endeavors in the following domains. If you are interested in learning more about our work, please feel free to contact us.
                    p We hope you enjoy reading them as much as we enjoyed writing them.
    // Report 1
    #ai-for-health.bg-half.pt-6
        .container.mb-lg-6.mb-md-5.mb-4
          .row
            .col-lg-4
              a(href='#')
                .bg-grayphite
                  .py-lg-7.px-lg-6.py-md-6.px-md-5.py-5.px-4
                    .text-black.pr-lg-4.text-center
                      h1.display-1.mb-1.font-weight-bolder 1
                      //h5 AI for Health
            .col-lg-8
              .bg-black
                .py-lg-7.px-lg-6.py-md-6.px-md-5.py-5.px-4
                  .text-white.pr-lg-4.lead
                    h2.mb-4 AI for Health
                    p.mb-4 The integration of XAI techniques into the health domain is not without its challenges. The complex nature of healthcare data, including its high dimensionality, heterogeneity, and temporal dependencies, presents unique difficulties in developing interpretable AI models. Additionally, the trade-off between interpretability and performance must be carefully balanced, as more complex models tend to be more accurate but less interpretable. Ensuring that the explanations generated by AI systems are understandable and actionable for healthcare professionals and patients alike poses another significant challenge.
                    div.pb-md-2.mt-4
                      a.btn.btn-outline-white(href="#") REQUEST ACCESS TO THE REPORT
    // Report 2
    #ai-for-finance.container.mb-lg-6.mb-md-5.mb-4
        .row
          .col-lg-4
            a(href='#')
              .bg-grayphite
                .py-lg-7.px-lg-6.py-md-6.px-md-5.py-5.px-4
                  .text-black.pr-lg-4.text-center
                    h1.display-1.mb-1.font-weight-bolder 2
                    //h5 LINE
          .col-lg-8
            .bg-yellow
              .py-lg-7.px-lg-6.py-md-6.px-md-5.py-5.px-4
                .text-black.pr-lg-4.lead
                  h2.mb-4 AI for Finance
                  p.mb-4 Explore our reports on the transformative power of AI in the financial sector. Learn about the applications of XAI in risk assessment, fraud detection, algorithmic trading, and portfolio management. We aim to foster transparency and accountability in financial decision-making processes, empowering both industry professionals and individual investors.
                  div.pb-md-2.mt-4
                    a.btn.btn-outline-black(href="#") REQUEST ACCESS TO THE REPORT

    //- Line 3
    #human-in-the-loop.container.mb-lg-6.mb-md-5.mb-4
      .row
          .col-lg-4
            a(href='#')
              .bg-grayphite
                .py-lg-7.px-lg-6.py-md-6.px-md-5.py-5.px-4
                  .text-black.pr-lg-4.text-center
                    h1.display-1.mb-1.font-weight-bolder 3
                    //h5 LINE
          .col-lg-8
            .bg-black
              .py-lg-7.px-lg-6.py-md-6.px-md-5.py-5.px-4
                .text-white.pr-lg-4.lead
                  h2.mb-4 Human in the loop
                  p.mb-4 Engage with our reports that delve into the concept of "Human in the Loop" AI systems. Discover how XAI techniques enable collaboration between humans and AI algorithms, allowing for better decision-making and leveraging the strengths of both parties. We investigate methods to enhance human understanding and control over AI systems, ensuring their safe and ethical deployment.
                  div.pb-md-2.mt-4
                    a.btn.btn-outline-white(href="#") REQUEST ACCESS TO THE REPORT
    //- Line 4
    #interactive-ai.container.mb-lg-6.mb-md-5.mb-4
        .row
          .col-lg-4
            a(href='line_4.html')
              .bg-grayphite
                .py-lg-7.px-lg-6.py-md-6.px-md-5.py-5.px-4
                  .text-black.pr-lg-4.text-center
                    h1.display-1.mb-1.font-weight-bolder 4
                    //h5 LINE
          .col-lg-8
            .bg-yellow
              .py-lg-7.px-lg-6.py-md-6.px-md-5.py-5.px-4
                .text-black.pr-lg-4.lead
                  h2.mb-4 Interactive AI
                  p.mb-4 We explore innovative approaches to enable users to interact and converse with AI systems effectively. Discover how XAI methodologies empower users to ask questions, seek explanations, and actively participate in the decision-making process. We strive to create AI systems that are not only powerful but also accessible and understandable to users.
                  div.pb-md-2.mt-4
                    a.btn.btn-outline-black(href="#") REQUEST ACCESS TO THE REPORT


